'''[[borax]] [[bead]] [[test]]'''
#{{chemistry}} in [[qualitative]] [[inorganic]] [[analysis]], a test for the [[presence]] of certain [[metallic]] [[element]]s by observing the [[colour]]s given to a bead of borax in a [[loop]] of [[platinum]] [[wire]] held in the [[oxidizing]] and [[reducing]] parts of a [[bunsen]] [[flame]]
